      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IDEAL AN ACE (4) comes here following a ninth behind Wake Up Geoff at Listed level two weeks ago over 2130m at Gloucester Park. Should enjoy a lovely run and looks the one to beat. BEAU TOULOUSE (11) broke last start and finished a distant eighth over 2190m at Northam when making his first appearance. Will need an ounce of luck to slot in from this tricky draw. Big chance if he behaves in this similar assignment. ZILLIONAIRE (2) faces the starter for the first time. By American Ideal and hails from the G Bond & S Bond stable. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. Placed in a recent trial and is well-placed to score at her first appearance. PARAGLIDER (7) is in the mix following a fifth at his most recent appearance over 2130m at Gloucester Park. Top-three candidate.",
